id.hub_intro.benefit_answer:
1. Jaminan Pesanan
2. Mitra Pengemudi Hub dapat memilih sendiri Area Hub dan Slot Jam Skema Hub 
Skema Hub bersifat opsional, sehingga Mitra Pengemudi dapat memilih sendiri cara menjalankan pesanan, baik secara reguler maupun melalui Skema Hub. Mitra Pengemudi Shopee tetap dapat menjalankan pesanan reguler di luar Slot Jam Skema Hub.
id.hub_intro.how_answer:
1. Mitra Pengemudi Shopee wajib membaca dan memahami 'Syarat & Ketentuan', sebelum memilih untuk 'Gabung Skema Hub' dan diproses ke dalam Skema Hub.
2. Setelah klik 'Gabung Skema Hub', Mitra Pengemudi Shopee dapat memilih Slot Jam Skema Hub yang tersedia dalam Area Hub.
3. Mitra Pengemudi Shopee wajib melihat informasi terkait Biaya Pengantaran, Kriteria Performa, dan Jaminan Pesanan yang akan diterima sebelum mendaftarkan diri dalam Slot Jam Skema Hub.
4. Mitra Pengemudi Shopee diharapkan untuk berkomitmen dan mematuhi Ketentuan Layanan Skema Hub saat bergabung dalam Skema Hub. Jika tidak, Mitra Pengemudi Shopee berpotensi dikenakan sanksi sesuai dengan Syarat & Ketentuan yang berlaku.

order.reason_guidance.report_issue.conte:
In the following situations:

- Unable to contact Recipient after 3 call attempts, spaced 5 mins apart.
- Recipient reschedules delivery.

Driver reports to change order status to ‘On-hold’, then keeps the parcel for re-delivery within 4 hours.

During this time, Driver can still handle new orders, or return this order as instructed below.

If redelivery to Recipient is unsuccessful, Driver can contact Sender to update them on the order status and arrange a return.
If Driver is unsuccessful to return to Sender, return the parcel to Company as instructed {here}.
Driver returns the parcel to Company when:

- Unable to contact Sender after 3 call attempts, spaced 5 mins apart.
- Sender rejects the return.

See the instructions {here}.
order.reason_guidance.return_to_sender.s:
If redelivery to Recipient is unsuccessful, Driver can contact Sender to update them on the order status and arrange a return.
If Driver is unsuccessful to return to Sender, return the parcel to Company as instructed {here}.

Driver returns the parcel to Company when:

- Unable to contact Sender after 3 call attempts, spaced 5 mins apart.
- Sender rejects the return.

See the instructions {here}.
In case you would like to re-deliver parcel to recipient, please choose [Cancel return] to proceed this order.
Please contact the seller to inform them and clarify returning reason.

If you fail to contact the seller after at least 3 attempts and having requested Return to seller, please return the package to ShopeeFood within the assigned time as following:

Choose "Cancel return" > Choose "Return goods to company"

Select or note the specific returning reason and time.

Collect returning fee after returning back the package to the seller.

In case the recipient contacts before submitting Return to ShopeeFood request, choose "Cancel return" > Choose "Cancel return to Seller" to continue.

In case the recipient contacts after submitting Return to ShopeeFood request, please go to Help Center > Search “Return packages” for more instructions.

*Batas nilai transaksi bulanan adalah jumlah uang yang masuk ke dalam saldo ShopeePay Anda melalui aktivitas Top up, transfer masuk dari akun ShopeePay lain, atau pengembalian dana (refund) yang Anda terima dalam bentuk ShopeePay.
